Subject: [PATCH v2 3/3] Drivers: hv: Never allocate anything besides framebuffer from framebuffer memory region
Date:   Thu, 25 Aug 2022 11:00:24 +0200
Message-Id: <20220825090024.1007883-4-vkuznets@redhat.com>
